자동화¶

In [130]:
def pie_plot(key, data):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
    cols = data.columns
    fig.suptitle('서울시 운동하지 않는 이유 - {key}', fontweight ="bold")
    for i in range(len(cols)):  
        plt.subplot(len(cols)+1, 2,i+1)
        plt.title(cols[i])
        plt.pie(data[cols[i]], labels = data[cols].index, autopct = '%.1f%%')
    
    plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0.03, 1, 0.95])
    plt.show()
In [131]:
# 데이터 전처리 자동화
drop_col = ['대분류', '기타']
grouped = DF3.groupby('대분류')

for key, group in grouped:
    df = grouped.get_group(key)
    df.drop(drop_col, axis =1, inplace = True)
    df.set_index('분류', inplace = True)
    pie_plot(key, df)
